            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:508px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/E1/53/wKgBEFpKLWKANO4LAB_5ZNggUmI32.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/E1/53/wKgBEFpKLWKANO4LAB_5ZNggUmI32.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278475744" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278475746" data-seq="278475747" data-pid="278475746" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278475746.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:508px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/E1/53/wKgBEFpKLWSAS5PRABwTxsHytog14.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/E1/53/wKgBEFpKLWSAS5PRABwTxsHytog14.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278475746" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278475751" data-seq="278475989" data-pid="278475751" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278475751.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:508px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/E1/54/wKgBEFpKLWWAWNhVABiakzdzWXg25.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/E1/54/wKgBEFpKLWWAWNhVABiakzdzWXg25.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278475751" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div data-seq="277887893" data-index="4" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t1"><span class="_j_anchor">day2 呀诺达1日游</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="279100904">
            早上7点35集合，我们6点50起床，可惜酒店早餐要7点半才有，郁闷。<br />
在外面随便买了点早餐，话说<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>真心宰外地人，一个早餐3个人吃了60，这边澳芒要30多块一斤。奉劝想来<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>买水果的死了这条心吧。真的不值。同样的东西在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>只要6块多一斤。<br />
等到接近7点50，车终于到了。
        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="279101766">
            等车的位置在凤凰岛大石头这里。旅游车是沿着海边<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196328.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚湾" target="_blank">三亚湾</a>路一路接人。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_279101489" data-seq="279101490" data-pid="279101489" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/279101489.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:508px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/AB/87/wKgBEFpM3rKAJXNbABAn5V4LH3g49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/AB/87/wKgBEFpM3rKAJXNbABAn5V4LH3g49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="279101489" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277888703">
            呀诺达是一个5A级热带雨林景区，根据导游介绍(我只记得几个感兴趣的点)，呀诺达是方言里的123的意思，他们打招呼的方式就是这个<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/88@2x.png" style="width:23px;" />，景区赋予它新的内涵，“呀”表示创新，“诺”表示承诺，“达”表示践行，同时“呀诺达”又被意为欢迎、你好，表示友好和祝福。<br />
呀诺达景区由团队耗巨资37个亿打造，位于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/25419.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="保亭" target="_blank">保亭</a>三道农场，堪称<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>钻石级热带雨林景区。景区内植被覆盖非常丰富。现在还在不断开发建设。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278125370" data-seq="278125371" data-pid="278125370" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278125370.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:508px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/28/0A/wKgBEFpIlaCAMHAfABxDLKiSo1072.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/28/0A/wKgBEFpIlaCAMHAfABxDLKiSo1072.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278125370" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278554503">
            昨晚在酒店推荐的蚂蜂窝app上，下了呀诺达1日游的单，现在看来是挺值的，150含了门票和接送，很划算。<br />
里面比较有意思的是一个踏瀑戏水的项目，蚂蜂窝上套餐类型很全，最终经过多方考虑，加上自己一点小小私心，定了2个普通，1个踏瀑戏水。虽然刚定完时媳妇颇有微词，不过后来证明我的选择是正确的。<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/1@2x.png" style="width:23px;" />。呀诺达的军事化管理的同时也很人性化。因为呀诺达景区进入是就要确认是走踏瀑戏水线路还是普通线路，当时还一直担心是否一上午都碰不到一起，而且下午踏瀑戏水线路的会重复上午普通线路的观景路线。后来，听说不玩踏瀑戏水的也可以陪同，走栈道即可，还能全程拍照，一下安心许多。<br />
旅行的意义就是家人一起欣赏美景美食，能够一起旅行，本身就是一种幸运。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278130212" data-seq="278130213" data-pid="278130212" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278130212.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:508px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/2A/A8/wKgBEFpImN-AbekjAAwKMOvAq0M81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/2A/A8/wKgBEFpImN-AbekjAAwKMOvAq0M81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278130212" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278477619">
            导游定下景区的集合点，我们出发了。
        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278458405">
            进入景区前，换上草鞋，带上头盔，准备好换的衣裳(踏瀑戏水湿身率几乎100%)，队伍教练带着我们向目标前进。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278459033" data-seq="278459034" data-pid="278459033" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278459033.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D8/72/wKgBEFpKHxuAR-GFAAmc5EtgLc434.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D8/72/wKgBEFpKHxuAR-GFAAmc5EtgLc434.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278459033" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278459909" data-seq="278459910" data-pid="278459909" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278459909.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:909px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D8/D2/wKgBEFpKH6aAQ6f0AA2yRADanXI59.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D8/D2/wKgBEFpKH6aAQ6f0AA2yRADanXI59.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278459909" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278460320">
            乘坐电瓶车15分钟左右，就到了踏瀑戏水项目的第一关。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278460540" data-seq="278460541" data-pid="278460540" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278460540.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D9/19/wKgBEFpKH_6AcEMXAAyLVhL_uAw49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D9/19/wKgBEFpKH_6AcEMXAAyLVhL_uAw49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278460540" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278460786">
            之前因为在网上找过攻略，还不算惊奇。<br />
但是没看过攻略的人，大部分就被第一关吓到了。<br />
要抓着铁环荡到对面还不能湿身。<br />
看着教练轻松荡过，有点跃跃欲试。但看着前面几人基本起跳就落水，感觉这个关卡也不是那么简单的。<br />
到我上阵后，想通过收腹来提升高度，结果还是失败了，荡过去，下半身都从<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/145826.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="水里" target="_blank">水里</a>过了。<br />
最后等我湿着过去后，教练又演示了一遍，原来，是要来个半圆运动从侧面绕一下，180转身下落，提升高度，直接腿着地。<br />
可惜等我知道，已经失去机会了。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278468169" data-seq="278468170" data-pid="278468169" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278468169.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/DD/26/wKgBEFpKJlGAJdEaAAxgkJobDY420.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/DD/26/wKgBEFpKJlGAJdEaAAxgkJobDY420.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278468169" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278465283">
            第二关是走轮胎，保持平衡，脚的落点是关键。<br />
难度不算大，只要踩着两个轮胎中间部位，保持住平衡就可以顺利通过。中间有几次惊险差点落水，用做娃娃操挺过来了。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278468256" data-seq="278468257" data-pid="278468256" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278468256.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/DD/31/wKgBEFpKJmaAXgyoAAzm0ShRSgI44.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/DD/31/wKgBEFpKJmaAXgyoAAzm0ShRSgI44.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278468256" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278480356">
            后面几关有穿越火线，走铁锁，独木桥，弹力网，相对都还比较简单。<br />
现代化的景区开发，让原本可以踏着石头顺溪而上的路途，都饱含了商业味道。<br />
踏着这些大石逆流而上时，让我回想起小时候老爸带着我还有几个姐姐一起探索家乡溪流和丛林的日子。那时老爸在前头带路，试探石块的结实程度和可行路径，我们紧随其后，一路考验体力耐力，惊险刺激的同时，也充满欢声笑语。那是多么珍贵的回忆啊。<br />
现在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16107.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="大城" target="_blank">大城</a>市的生活，繁重的工作在挤压了生活时间，臃肿的身体也让我缺少了探险的激情和活力。<br />
唯有怀着一颗不老的心，仍旧在生活的夹缝中寻求到一丝的解脱。找到心灵的一些慰藉，为梦想保留一点空间，同时放松自己，迎接更大的挑战。<br />

        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278481569">
            轻松通过中间关卡后，到了项目最后一关，攀岩瀑布。<br />
其实也难度不大，绳索和脚蹬也提前都设置好了，基本按路线走都不会有什么危险性，也能够很轻松抵达终点。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278483427" data-seq="278483428" data-pid="278483427" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278483427.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/E5/A1/wKgBEFpKM7OAE1HXAA1ueCNg-8E69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/E5/A1/wKgBEFpKM7OAE1HXAA1ueCNg-8E69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278483427" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278553419">
            过关的间隙，与家人一路吃吃喝喝，好不快哉！<br />
值得一提的是，呀诺达景区的管理模式统一了水果售价，一律10元一份。基本每个休息站我们都补给点水果饮料，还买了个冰淇淋，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>的水果甜度比北方高多了，女儿非常爱吃，每次吃的不亦乐乎。其实，每次吃东西的时候，女儿都非常爱吃，十足的小吃货一枚，这方面充分继承了我和她妈妈的优良基因，嘿嘿~<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/2@2x.png" style="width:23px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278553629" data-seq="278553630" data-pid="278553629" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278553629.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/0C/A7/wKgBEFpKyaqAVU1BAAalTp_lvzE85.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/0C/A7/wKgBEFpKyaqAVU1BAAalTp_lvzE85.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278553629" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278554271">
            上午结束后，在领取行李的地方，景区还配置了免费姜汤，点个赞<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/28@2x.png" style="width:23px;" />，为湿身的游客预防感冒，很贴心~<br />

        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278554737">
            中午景区有自费的雨林养生自助餐，因为之前在网上了解到，味道不咋地，就没参加。问了一下中午吃饭的事情，工作人员推荐到酒店里点菜。<br />
换装后，辗转到了雨林1号酒店，一下被这里的美景惊呆了。<br />
门口一个偌大的泳池，水清澈透亮，背靠大山，群树环绕，景色秀丽，绝对是个养生休假绝佳去处。房费标间788含双早含景区门票2张，听起来很划算。不过就是有点小噪音，屋顶上方就是索道，若是有人滑下来会有点噪音。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278555419" data-seq="278555420" data-pid="278555419" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278555419.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/0D/C1/wKgBEFpK0NWAV2pVAAorDzw82B035.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/0D/C1/wKgBEFpK0NWAV2pVAAorDzw82B035.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278555419" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278556042" data-seq="278556043" data-pid="278556042" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8181974/278556042.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:508px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/0E/25/wKgBEFpK0pyAbpvQABT8FdZKDrs92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/0E/25/wKgBEFpK0pyAbpvQABT8FdZKDrs92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278556042" alt="" />
        </a>
